title: TeamTreeHouse - Rails Development Complete
description:
The Rails Development Track, from Treehouse, Provides you with the essential training All you need to be A Rails Developer. In fact, it explores much more than just Rails. It starts off by you Giving A Solid Grounding in HTML, CSS and javascript - and Also Gives you A Chance to Closely EXAMINE the Ruby Language Itself. thing About The Great Rails Development is it That Provides All the training you need Preliminary in HTML, CSS and javascript - which are all very relevant in Rails. On the other hand, you can choose to skip these parts if you only want to learn Ruby. Courses that are part of : 

How to Make a Website
Introduction to Programming
javascript Foundations
Console Foundations
Git Basics
Installing a Ruby Development Environment
Ruby Foundations
Build a Todo List Application with Rails 4
Database Foundations
ActiveRecord Basics
User Authentication with Rails
